title: Moe Williams with PA & Charch
description: Former Vikings RB Moe Williams spent almost his entire career with the purple, and his time in MN included a memorable 2004 Wildcard playoff game against the Packers, in which he opened scoring with a long TD on the opening drive...he shares memories and talks football with PA & Charch!
